{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048340/extras/title.png?t=1738520571\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play a variety of different retro-inspired mini games, as if it were a gaming night out in the 1980s/90s!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048340/extras/goofgif2.gif?t=1738520571\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Go from classic pinball, to puzzles, to platformers, to shoot-'em-ups, maze chasers, adventure games, a rhythm game (with a custom song editor!), PLUS point-and-click games, tabletop games, billiards, and even some gambling! Unlock each mini game one by one as you go along.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048340/extras/goofgif3.gif?t=1738520571\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete all of the mini games while getting to the absolute highest score that you can possibly reach! There's even an option to play with classic CRT display/VHS filters, to make the '80s arcade theme feel really authentic! PLUS, the mini games have all-time high score leaderboards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A playthrough of this game is about 3-4 hours long, so it\u2019s rather mini \u2014 but it\u2019s extremely replayable and jam-packed with tons of fun! You\u2019ll have to check back in every once in a while if you want to keep your spot on the high score leaderboards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Starring the one and only Goofer the Gopher, It's an indie bonanza extravaganza!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">(NOTE: I can only promise an English  (and maybe Swedish) version of the game available by launch date. However I am getting in contact with translators so that other languages can be available ASAP! Thank you for understanding)</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to the arcade!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3048340/57ec21c71a5f64056b5d5b3d23254c0d59f87142.jpg"},{"name":"Congrats, GAME OVER!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3048340/8aef0cd89c3a609d9db7863f03ff4e515c5fff34.jpg"},{"name":"Coin Catch \u2014 GOAL","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3048340/13afed351ff50eba0375aed2cadb4f134d799778.jpg"},{"name":"Coin Catch \u2014 MASTER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3048340/b0d62655ea820d5ed5f1270621611c02be46d16f.jpg"},{"name":"Jumper \u2014 GOAL","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3048340/f65b1e319a7891cce80c7b05cfd5312be6341d39.jpg"},{"name":"Jumper \u2014 MASTER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3048340/4a204fc423b7b0e50d9c55483778c11a8fcf1f96.jpg"},{"name":"Recker \u2014 GOAL","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3048340/b2b8e33b033f0f774724709719d36693cae0e0f8.jpg"},{"name":"Recker \u2014 MASTER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3048340/d0d04809b85b309dfb5e72465a016db81f148106.jpg"},{"name":"Laser Launch \u2014 GOAL","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3048340/3343ea6963ec75643f35d49c79dd82f198e18788.jpg"},{"name":"Laser Launch \u2014 MASTER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3048340/e66d9b1addf073108fbdb1060e4c69ff825672cc.jpg"}],"total":50},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048340/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738520571","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048340/page.bg.jpg?t=1738520571","capsule_image":"https: